Package: credMortality
Title: Reproducible Supplement for Credibility-Based Sub-Population Mortality Forecasting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Gabriele", family = "Pittarello", email = "pwt887@ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible code supplement accompanying the manuscript
    "Forecasting Sub-Population Mortality Using Credibility Theory".
    The package provides data preparation, model fitting, forecasting,
    performance assessment, and figure-generation functions used in the
    manuscript's computational workflow.
